The Sangguniang Bayan to review and authorize the supplemental budget identified in item 2. Additionally, clearly identify PBCC as a local economic enterprise of the municipality;
The management to submit the foregoing documents to the audit team for our further evaluation; and,
5) Stop, henceforth, the improper practice of treating subsidies and other receipts favorable to PBCC as funds held in trust.

